{"version": 2, "width": 1, "height": 1, "timestamp": 1774963156, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "SwarmCode — Real-time networking between Claude Code instances"}
[0.919683, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.920439, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;141m  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;141m  ║           SwarmCode — Live Demo                       ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;141m  ║   Real-time messaging between Claude Code instances    ║\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;141m  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2mRedis: redis://192.168.4.161:30379\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mCleaning up...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.935076, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.935209, "o", "\u001b[1m  Step 1: Workspaces come online\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.43866, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1m[desktop-api]\u001b[0m \u001b[2mon desktop\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.449099, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:17\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114mregistered\u001b[0m — \"Building REST API for user auth\"\r\n"]
[2.253019, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1m[laptop-frontend]\u001b[0m \u001b[2mon laptop\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.253272, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:18\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114mregistered\u001b[0m — \"Building React frontend\"\r\n"]
[3.254618, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m  Step 2: Desktop builds API, notifies laptop\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.254735, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.755754, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:20\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m  Building POST /api/users endpoint...\r\n"]
[5.26318, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:21\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m \u001b[2m→ laptop-frontend\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.263313, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m         \u001b[0m  \u001b[2m\"POST /api/users is live. Schema: { id, email, name, role }. Auth via JWT.\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.264653, "o", "\r\n"]
[6.264808, "o", "\u001b[1m  Step 3: Laptop receives message, asks a question\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.769271, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:23\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;221m← 1 message(s) received\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.27047, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:23\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m  \u001b[2mProcessing: \"POST /api/users is live. Schema: { id: uuid, email...\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.276262, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:24\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m \u001b[2m→ desktop-api\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m         \u001b[0m  \u001b[2m\"Got it! Building the signup form. Does /api/users support pagination?\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.276752, "o", "\r\n"]
[9.276893, "o", "\u001b[1m  Step 4: Desktop receives question, answers instantly\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.78204, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:26\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;221m← 1 message(s) received\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.590183, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:26\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m \u001b[2m→ laptop-frontend\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m         \u001b[0m  \u001b[2m\"Yes! GET /api/users?page=1&limit=20. Also adding GET /api/users/:id.\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.591659, "o", "\r\n"]
[11.59179, "o", "\u001b[1m  Step 5: Desktop shares API schema as artifact\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.099283, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:28\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m \u001b[2m→ *broadcast*\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.099432, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m         \u001b[0m  \u001b[2m\"Shared artifact \"user-api-schema\" — TypeScript interfaces for all endpoints\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.604012, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:28\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;221m← 2 message(s) received\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.604186, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:28\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;80mRetrieved artifact → generating TypeScript types\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.605525, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m  Step 6: Laptop confirms integration complete\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.605681, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[14.111256, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:30\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114m\u001b[1mlaptop-frontend\u001b[0m \u001b[2m→ desktop-api\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[38;5;244m         \u001b[0m  \u001b[2m\"Signup + login done. JWT auth working. Pagination integrated. Ready for review.\"\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[14.615898, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:30\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;221m← 1 message(s) received\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[14.616087, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m08:19:30\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;75m\u001b[1mdesktop-api\u001b[0m  \u001b[38;5;114mAcknowledged — frontend integration complete\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.116821, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.116982, "o", "  \u001b[38;5;244m───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[38;5;141m  Demo complete!\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m6 messages exchanged in real-time between desktop and laptop.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mNo copy-pasting. No manual coordination. Agents talked directly.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.117066, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[1mInstall:\u001b[0m  npm install -g swarmcode-mcp\r\n  \u001b[1mSetup:\u001b[0m    swarmcode init my-workspace --redis redis://your-host:6379\r\n  \u001b[1mGitHub:\u001b[0m   https://github.com/spranab/swarmcode\r\n\r\n"]
